-----------------------------------
CONTAQ  82C596  386/486 WriteBack 
-----------------------------------

NOTICE!  Contaq's original definition of REG_17 required b5:0 = 27H.
         Versions V080B41x immediately below initialize per this rule.
         Some M/Boards do NOT work with this setting.  Some do.

         Contaq's later definition of REG_17 requires b5:0 = 22H.
         Versions V080B42x further below initialize per this new rule.
         All M/Boards we tested DO work with this setting.

>>--->   As a rule:  TRY USING VERSIONS '42x FIRST  !!!

         If neither setting works right, and you've figured out some
         value for these "magic bits" that works, call us and we'll
         cook a bios to your liking!
         

Filename   Port      Description  '596 Single-Chip WB, REG_17 = 27
--------   -------   ---------------------------------------------------------
V080B410   CNTQ410   386/486/Cx	  REV-A
V080B411   CNTQ411   386/486/Cx   REV-A  Layout: Cyrix #A20M #FLUSH
V080B412   CNTQ412   386/486/Cx   REV-A  Layout: Cyrix #A20M #FLUSH, Fast-A20

V080B417   CNTQ417   386/486/Cx   REV-0


Filename   Port      Description  '596 Single-Chip WB, REG_17 = 22
--------   -------   ---------------------------------------------------------
V080B420   CNTQ420   386/486/Cx	  REV-A
V080B421   CNTQ421   386/486/Cx   REV-A  Layout: Cyrix #A20M #FLUSH
V080B422   CNTQ422   386/486/Cx   REV-A  Layout: Cyrix #A20M #FLUSH, Fast-A20

V080B427   CNTQ427   386/486/Cx   REV-0



